    "title": "Wafilipi 1:1–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "50001001-50001011",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108102\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Paulo</span> alikuwa mtu wa kwanza kuwaambia watu wa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108126\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Filipi</span> kuhusu <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108219\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Yesu</span>. Hadithi kuhusu hili imeandikwa katika Matendo sura ya 16.</p><p>Baada ya Paulo kuondoka Filipi, viongozi wengine na <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108100\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">mashemasi</span> waliendelea kusaidia <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108096\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">kanisa</span>.</p><p>Maombi ya <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108227\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Paulo</span> kwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108077\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">waumini</span> wa Wafilipi yalikuwa yamejaa furaha. Alibaki marafiki wa karibu sana nao. Walikuwa washirika wake katika kueneza <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108043\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">habari njema</span> kuhusu Yesu.</p><p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108199\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Mungu</span> alifanya kazi katika <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108419\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">mioyo</span> ya waumini na kufanya mema kupitia wao. Paulo aliwaombea waendelee kuishi jinsi Yesu alivyofundisha watu kuishi. Kisha watakuwa tayari kwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108065\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">kurudi kwa Yesu</span>.</p>",
